fields.question: How to book a parking spot?
fields.answer: You can book a parking spot through our website or mobile app. You need to register and choose a convenient spot from available ones.

fields.question: What payment methods are available?
fields.answer: We accept cash, credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, MIR), and electronic wallets. Payment can be made one-time or by subscription.

fields.question: Are there discounts for regular customers?
fields.answer: Yes, we have a discount system for regular customers. A 15% discount is provided for monthly parking payment in advance. Special offers are also available on weekends.

fields.question: How does the video surveillance system work?
fields.answer: The parking lot is equipped with a modern video surveillance system that operates 24/7. Recordings are stored for 30 days. Access to recordings is provided upon request.

fields.question: Can I leave my car for a long period?
fields.answer: Yes, we provide long-term car storage service. Special rates and additional car maintenance services are available.

fields.question: What additional services are available?
fields.answer: We offer a wide range of additional services: car washing, electric vehicle charging, tire storage, body polishing, interior cleaning, and more.

fields.question: How does the parking access system work?
fields.answer: Parking access is granted through an electronic pass or mobile app. First-time visitors need to register at the reception.

fields.question: What to do in case of car damage?
fields.answer: If you discover any damage to your car, immediately report it to the parking administrator. We will conduct an investigation using the video surveillance system.

fields.question: Is there a car towing service?
fields.answer: Yes, we provide car towing service in case of breakdown. The service cost depends on the distance and car type.

fields.question: How to cancel a booking?
fields.answer: You can cancel a booking through the website or mobile app at least 2 hours before the parking start time. A penalty fee may be charged for late cancellation.
